### 创建笔记
POST http://localhost:8080/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "测试笔记",
  "content": "这是我写的第一条笔记"
}

### 获取所有笔记
GET http://localhost:8080/notes

### 获取单条笔记
GET http://localhost:8080/notes/1

### 更新笔记
PUT http://localhost:8080/notes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "更新后的标题",
  "content": "这是更新后的内容"
}

### 删除笔记
DELETE http://localhost:8080/notes/1
